                        <note n="1" xml:id="note-t-1">
                            

<p>Theo had turned 16 on 1 May.</p>
                        </note>
                        
                    
                        <note n="2" xml:id="note-t-2">
                            

<p><rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#_399">Uncle Hein</rs> and <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#_1613">Aunt Mietje</rs> moved to Laken, near Brussels; their names were removed from the Brussels civil register on 30 April.</p>
                        </note>
                        
                    
